Package logic.gameObjects

Class ThanosTest2

  • java.lang.Object
    • logic.TestUsingController
      • logic.gameObjects.ThanosTest2
  • public class ThanosTest2
extends TestUsingController
    Tests for the Thanos class. This class extends TestUsingController which is different in the class ThanosTest (it extends TestUsingModel). Therefore this class tests the thanosTurn() method which needs a valid controller object to work.
    Author:
    Luka Stoehr
